1
00:00:56,287 --> 00:01:00,262
=The Demon=

2
00:01:00,587 --> 00:01:03,250
=Episode 23=

3
00:01:39,322 --> 00:01:40,660
♪Parasol leaves fall♪

4
00:01:40,660 --> 00:01:41,910
♪A lonely shadow under the moon♪

5
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:43,785
♪A refreshing evening breeze♪

6
00:01:46,335 --> 00:01:47,760
♪Those whispers♪

7
00:01:47,822 --> 00:01:48,972
♪Still echo♪

8
00:01:49,072 --> 00:01:51,262
♪In my heart♪

9
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,200
Looks like

10
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,599
Dayao has erased herself

11
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,000
from everyone's mind.

12
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:58,239
Luckily,

13
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,760
I still remember her.

14
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:05,079
♪Can't shake it from my mind,
it all ends in nothingness♪

15
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:06,120
Well,

16
00:02:06,439 --> 00:02:08,080
what's your plan after this?

17
00:02:08,462 --> 00:02:10,722
♪You're the sleepless wind chime♪

18
00:02:10,797 --> 00:02:12,097
♪Stirring all my thoughts♪

19
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,199
This is a vast world.

20
00:02:14,310 --> 00:02:15,785
♪Spring comes, autumn goes♪

21
00:02:15,785 --> 00:02:17,199
♪Sun and Moon turn in cycles,
that unendurable winter♪

22
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,319
Naturally, there's a place for me.

23
00:02:19,222 --> 00:02:21,175
♪The unmelting ice♪

24
00:02:21,272 --> 00:02:22,737
♪No matter how far I go, you remain♪

25
00:02:22,737 --> 00:02:24,697
♪The scenery I cannot reach♪

26
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,520
There must be a place

27
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:28,395
for you

28
00:02:28,397 --> 00:02:30,225
♪You are the liquor of sorrow
that breaks the heart♪

29
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,960
in this wild world.

30
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:32,972
♪Drunk yet awake♪

31
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,319
Your Highness...

32
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:02,800
You can't go in, Your Highness.

33
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,840
Shen Wangchen!

34
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:04,780
♪Parasol leaves fall♪

35
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,360
Your Highness...

36
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,280
Shen Wangchen!

37
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,080
Step aside!

38
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,919
You can't go in.

39
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,080
Shen Wangchen!

40
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:09,759
Your Highness...

41
00:03:09,759 --> 00:03:10,639
Shen Wangchen!

42
00:03:11,087 --> 00:03:12,250
♪Those whispers♪

43
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,280
Listen here.

44
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:14,639
If you don't marry me,

45
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:16,639
you won't be the city lord for long.

46
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,120
I'll give you another chance.

47
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:21,319
If you are to take my hand,

48
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:23,759
I'll help you by persuading the court.

49
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:24,479
See the guest out.

50
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,599
You...

51
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:28,719
♪Can't shake it from my mind,
it all ends in nothingness♪

52
00:03:28,719 --> 00:03:29,520
Shen Wangchen!

53
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,080
I'm warning you.

54
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,199
If you refuse to marry me,

55
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,319
I'll annihilate your clan!

56
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:35,356
♪You're the sleepless wind chime♪

57
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:36,912
♪Stirring all my thoughts♪

58
00:03:36,912 --> 00:03:38,862
♪You're the shooting star
who lights my loneliness♪

59
00:03:39,012 --> 00:03:40,362
♪Spring comes, autumn goes♪

60
00:03:40,362 --> 00:03:43,412
♪Sun and Moon turn in cycles,
that unendurable winter♪

61
00:03:43,787 --> 00:03:44,900
♪The unmelting ice♪

62
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,960
Tanghulu for sale!

63
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,080
Will you be able

64
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,599
to have a long trip?

65
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,599
I will.

66
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:52,560
What a brilliant idea from our son.

67
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,637
Upon learning

68
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:55,360
about his plan of taking me on a trip,

69
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,680
I've felt

70
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:58,240
all fine.

71
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,080
Well,

72
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,039
you should've heeded his advice sooner

73
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,319
and gone on a trip.

74
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:05,439
Indeed.

75
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,560
I should've taken you

76
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,039
on a trip sooner.

77
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:10,560
It's just that I had been occupied
with work.

78
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:12,319
You've done a lot

79
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,400
for our family all these years.

80
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:16,120
So it's time

81
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:17,759
to take you on a trip.

82
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,720
Do it now

83
00:04:18,840 --> 00:04:20,361
or we'd be too old for that.

84
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,639
Come on. The carriage is ready.

85
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,279
Let's go.

86
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:26,262
♪Sun and Moon turn in cycles,
that unendurable winter♪

87
00:04:26,462 --> 00:04:28,262
♪The unmelting ice♪

88
00:04:28,312 --> 00:04:29,687
♪No matter how far I go, you remain♪

89
00:04:29,775 --> 00:04:31,787
♪The scenery I cannot reach♪

90
00:04:31,862 --> 00:04:35,512
♪You are countless threads,
an unbroken dream♪

91
00:04:35,875 --> 00:04:36,902
♪You are the liquor of sorrow♪

92
00:04:36,903 --> 00:04:38,425
♪That breaks the heart♪

93
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:40,100
♪Drunk yet awake♪

94
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,399
How about this?

95
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,519
This is lovely!

96
00:04:58,060 --> 00:05:01,412
(One year later)

97
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,680
Could you clean here too?

98
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,560
Thank you.

99
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,720
Thank you for the effort.

100
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,079
Hurry up.

101
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,399
You're taking forever.

102
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,040
Check this out, honey.

103
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:17,959
What do you think?

104
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:21,319
"Words can't express

105
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:23,480
how much he misses Dayao in Spring".

106
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,199
How are you finding it?

107
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,079
What a nice poem.

108
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,319
It's an acrostic, no less.

109
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:29,160
My wife really is cultured.

110
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:30,199
Of course I am.

111
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:31,279
Come on. Slowly.

112
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,720
Let's go.

113
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:33,680
This

114
00:05:33,759 --> 00:05:35,560
is where our chief often rests.

115
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,439
Well,

116
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:39,519
can I try it?

117
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,519
Go ahead.

118
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:48,519
I did it, Mother!

119
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:50,360
I can feel Chief Fan!

120
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:52,199
That's enough.

121
00:05:52,519 --> 00:05:53,879
You've felt it.

122
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,560
Don't make it dirty again.

123
00:05:56,519 --> 00:05:58,240
When the chief returns,

124
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,879
she still needs to use it.

125
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,439
Is the chief coming back?

126
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,800
Isn't she dead?

127
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,839
Watch your mouth!

128
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,560
Say that again!

129
00:06:16,319 --> 00:06:17,120
Yes, kick him!

130
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,800
Do it!

131
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,279
City Lord.

132
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,639
Is it necessary

133
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,959
to detour to the capital?

134
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:58,720
This sandstorm...

135
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:01,000
The sandstorm is growing stronger.

136
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,160
There are no houses around here.

137
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,639
Not even an inn.

138
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,759
Why don't we take another route?

139
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:06,759
We might still make it in time.

140
00:08:52,687 --> 00:08:57,712
(Directed by Yang Tai)

141
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,519
Well,

142
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,159
why did you help me?

143
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,360
You...

144
00:09:20,198 --> 00:09:21,478
Does he suffer from

145
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,879
some kind of speech disorder?

146
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:30,480
Dayao.

147
00:09:30,639 --> 00:09:31,919
Here's a letter from Mr. Shen.

148
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:32,399
I said,

149
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:33,480
I'll never believe

150
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,360
that human again.

151
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,320
Get lost!

152
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,480
(My father is gravely ill.)

153
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,790
(I couldn't manage to bid farewell.)

154
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,759
(Please wait for me.)

155
00:11:21,925 --> 00:11:25,588
♪Where did I lose my direction?♪

156
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:28,313
♪Only emptiness is left♪

157
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:33,475
♪Restless, sleepless, we part ways♪

158
00:11:33,613 --> 00:11:36,338
♪As sorrow slowly grows within♪

159
00:11:37,438 --> 00:11:40,925
♪Tears can't heal, smiles still ache♪

160
00:11:41,300 --> 00:11:44,550
♪Because my heart's with you♪

161
00:11:45,175 --> 00:11:50,000
♪Your gaze melted the haze♪

162
00:11:51,450 --> 00:11:58,313
♪Waiting so long for your return♪

163
00:11:59,175 --> 00:12:06,463
♪The setting sun reminds me of you♪

164
00:12:06,963 --> 00:12:11,875
♪If the clear sky is torn
by storm and rain one day♪

165
00:12:12,225 --> 00:12:15,025
♪Tears will flow♪

166
00:12:16,163 --> 00:12:21,800
♪I will still wait here with no regrets♪

167
00:12:22,475 --> 00:12:29,663
♪Waiting so long for your return♪

168
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:37,350
♪The setting sun reminds me of you♪

169
00:12:37,950 --> 00:12:42,638
♪In the amber desert,
you turn away with tears in your eyes♪

170
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:46,425
♪I'll welcome you back in a red dress♪

171
00:12:47,038 --> 00:12:52,925
♪Waiting forever with no regrets♪

172
00:12:54,638 --> 00:13:02,213
♪Waiting forever with no regrets♪
